		    <td width="90%" class="text"><p>Ambitious young professionals from around the world dream of coming to  the United States. CSB Trainee Program allows American host companies to take  advantage of this desire and access a world of talent. US companies can choose  from a select group of experienced young trainees -- at no cost --through this  unique exchange program.</p>
		      <p>There are notable benefits for businesses hosting participants of the  CSB Trainee Program. </p>
		      <ul>
		        <li><strong>Qualified  Candidates</strong><br>
		          Each participant is screened and interviewed in their home country and again by  CSB. Participants generally are bilingual (at least), have had at least one  year of experience in their field of training, and are eager to learn more  about American business and culture</li>
	          </ul>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Savings  on Taxes and Benefits</strong> <br>
                  American companies do not incur any recruiting and visa fees as the CSB Program  is fully  participant funded. It already includes the required  health and travel insurance. Additionally, CSB trainees are exempt from  Social Security, Medicare, and Unemployment taxes.              </li>
              </ul>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>No  Paperwork Hassle</strong><br>
                CSB will assist with preparation of all necessary visa application documents </li>
              </ul>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Globalizing  Your Workplace</strong><br>
                Join the CSB program to  add an  international perspective to your workplace by training highly  qualified and carefully screened bilingual or multilingual young professionals! </li>
              </ul>
<p>If you would like further information about the CSB Trainee Program, please  follow the link below to download the Host Company Handbook. You can also email  us at <a href="mailto:craig@csb-usa.com">craig@csb-usa.com</a> and someone  from our office will contact you.</p>
